{"type":"message","id":"3d37d537","parentId":"98fdafa2","timestamp":"2026-03-27T23:28:58.304Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session found is the cron job itself. There are no active user conversations in the last 5 minutes. So I should proceed with the autonomous learning task - searching for industry trends about enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services.\n\nLet me search for the latest trends in these areas.","thinkingSignature":"550a1efe9d3ef1dfb7b6ed832b93aedfb09d561bb1fc230727b98c5c6993cdc5"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到只有当前cron任务会话，无活跃用户对话。执行自主学习任务。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7rbs8w3qxsfo_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":859,"output":128,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44968,"cost":{"input":0.0002577,"output":0.0001536,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017307299999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774654134710}}
