{"type":"message","id":"a5d03f73","parentId":"59fa6a33","timestamp":"2026-03-27T23:30:14.979Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've completed the autonomous learning task. Let me summarize what was done.","thinkingSignature":"943995bd04a19d89e1931010fd59cfddc80695b89ad23f386c7e8236ab59ee17"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n✅ 自主学习已完成\n\n**执行摘要**：\n- 无活跃用户对话，触发自主学习\n- 搜索范围：企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成与IT运维服务\n- 整理关键信息4条\n- 已保存至 `memory/学习笔记.md`\n\n**核心要点**：\n1. **AI Agent** 从单点辅助走向全业务协同，多智能体协作生态成为主流\n2. **智能安防** 规模预计突破2800亿元，AI驱动的主动预判成主流，民用市场占比超45%\n3. **IT运维** 从AIOps向Agentic AIOps升级，40%以上大型企业将部署AI运维系统\n4. **网络集成** AI原生网络、运维Copilot、数字孪生是技术趋势\n\n笔记已整理为4大板块，可供姚总随时查阅参考。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5097,"output":202,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49280,"cost":{"input":0.0015291,"output":0.00024239999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00309093}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774654208883}}
